{"tid":1530431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[蘋果新聞員工請入] 訂閱建議","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T16:57:21.000Z","uid":113164,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1e9a6226685051203f9eddffea7ba6ff0cad2bca","tid":1530431,"uid":113164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:11:32.000Z","msg":"今日就開始正式收費，我自己都有訂閱左以示支持，唔想黨報獨大。<br />\n雖然收費唔係話貴，但身邊家人就會覺得，1個人俾左錢支持，另1個再俾多份就好似差緊少少，就好似買份報紙番屋企都可以share黎睇。<br />\n<br />\n個人建議可以增加一啲家庭plan (就好似spotify咁, 唔好理啲人點樣夾)，人數可以set 2-4人，每個數量價錢都不一，但平過就咁逐個逐個人去訂閱。<br />\n<br />\n雖然整體數入會有些微影響，但係都可以靠有心人去損錢頂住呀。唔想有人因為少少錢而唔去睇生果轉睇其他報紙..<br />\n<br />\n原諒1999，希望少少建議能夠令更多人去睇生果，唔睇HK10, 方向等黨報。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4298544c1666d5e984676e0b9c7cd358cea6ef","tid":1530431,"uid":113164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a11d522678a70c489a3778724206822050900e1","tid":1530431,"uid":264529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:20:46.000Z","msg":"HK01阿<br />\n最好活動先要收費，鬥01"},{"pid":"d4e800bf3cd14d368efcf9fdf52f5ff9a4645e9c","tid":1530431,"uid":113164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65de617d187c7b5832a6acb66452067e3bdfdde","tid":1530431,"uid":113164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d208270703e0c17828ea18340fd61c0732dc6024","tid":1530431,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"你地登入埋同一個account咪得"},{"pid":"ef4542c661ca32045753ab2e7f17a0550fefe805","tid":1530431,"uid":113164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d208270703e0c17828ea18340fd61c0732dc6024","